{#
/**
 * @file
 * bubblecard
 *
 * Available variables for bubblecard:
 *    - bubblecard.variable_name [variable_type]: Description of the variable. Example below.
 *    - bubblecard.invert [bool]: When set, colors will be inverted for light display on dark background.
 */
